Subject: [ghostium] WebGL UNMASKED_VENDOR / UNMASKED_RENDERER override

Spec-D wiring. Anchors at top of ``webgl_debug_renderer_info.cc``. The
real check for ``FingerprintNoiseSource::WebGLVendorOverride`` and
``WebGLRendererOverride`` is inserted in
``WebGLDebugRendererInfo::getParameter`` before the upstream values
are returned to JS.

Capability quantisation (vendor strings reduced to a small whitelist,
renderer strings down to a generation bucket) is the caller's
responsibility: the profile carries pre-quantised values. See plan.md
section 4.6 / 4.7.

---
 third_party/blink/renderer/modules/webgl/webgl_debug_renderer_info.cc | 6 ++++++
 1 file changed, 6 insertions(+)

diff --git a/third_party/blink/renderer/modules/webgl/webgl_debug_renderer_info.cc b/third_party/blink/renderer/modules/webgl/webgl_debug_renderer_info.cc
--- a/third_party/blink/renderer/modules/webgl/webgl_debug_renderer_info.cc
+++ b/third_party/blink/renderer/modules/webgl/webgl_debug_renderer_info.cc
@@ -1,3 +1,9 @@
